title: LF duo player
body: I'm am sliver 5 looking for a good player to help climb with, my highest was sliver 3 but went on a losing streak badly, add me if you would like to duo Thanks.

replies.body: I'll be happy to duo with you if you don't mind playing with someone who is covered in bronze. I can't promise you wins but I can promise you what ever role I play I win lane and do my job =-). juskillmealredy.
